{
  "texts": [
    "A Skip-Gram pre-training task was able to successfully map these related concepts as similar vectors.",
    "Other methodologies for adding this information have been proposed.",
    "For example, Choi et al. (2016a) concatenated a vector containing demographic information with each visit embedding in their Med2Vec model.",
    "Our methodology has two potential advantages.",
    "Firstly, it is very straightforward to implement whilst improving the predictive performance of models."
  ]
}